OL,3,C'I had a beautiful life': Filmmaker on
OL,4,Ccapturing war in Gaza
OL,6,FMohammed Abu Safia is a Palestinian
OL,7,Fjournalist and filmmaker who has been
OL,8,Fcovering the conflict in Gaza for ITV
OL,9,FNews since October 7.
OL,11,FNow one year on, Mohammed reflects on
OL,12,Fhis experience balancing his reporting
OL,13,Fon the war with looking after his
OL,14,Fyoung family.
OL,16,FTranslation by Humam Husari
OL,18,FBefore October 7, I had a beautiful
OL,19,Flife.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/27
