OL,3,C'I had a beautiful life': Filmmaker on
OL,4,Ccapturing war in Gaza
OL,6,FI worked as a freelance journalist and
OL,7,Ffixer, and I was also a project
OL,8,Fcoordinator for people with
OL,9,Fdisabilities, specifically amputees in
OL,10,Fa paracycling team called Sunbirds
OL,11,FGaza.
OL,13,FSaturday was always a special day for
OL,14,Fme - Friday was family time with the
OL,15,Fkids, but Saturday was always my day.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/27
