OL,3,C'I had a beautiful life': Filmmaker on
OL,4,Ccapturing war in Gaza
OL,6,FBut Saturday, October 7 was different.
OL,7,FI had planned to distribute wedding
OL,8,Finvitations for my friend Atiya's
OL,9,Fupcoming wedding. We were going to
OL,10,Fvisit all our mutual friends and
OL,11,Finvite them together.
OL,13,FBut that morning, nothing went as
OL,14,Fplanned. It was as if the gates of
OL,15,Fhell had opened on Gaza, a firestorm
OL,16,Fno one could understand.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/27
