OL,3,C'I had a beautiful life': Filmmaker on
OL,4,Ccapturing war in Gaza
OL,6,FMy wife and kids were at their
OL,7,Fgrandparents' house, and I was at my
OL,8,Fparents' place. My phone started
OL,9,Fringing like crazy - friends,
OL,10,Fjournalists, relatives. I wanted to
OL,11,Fimmediately go to the border and
OL,12,Fdocument what was happening with my
OL,13,Fcamera.
OL,15,FI then received a call from my older
OL,16,Fbrother, Jayyab. Due to his experience
OL,17,Fand work in journalism, he gave me
OL,18,Fsafety instructions, telling me not to
OL,19,Fgo to the border, that my safety was
OL,20,Fmore important than any picture.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/27
