OL,3,C'I had a beautiful life': Filmmaker on
OL,4,Ccapturing war in Gaza
OL,6,FHe emphasised safety protocols because
OL,7,Fhe knows how impulsive I can be.
OL,9,FAmong the calls I received was one
OL,10,Ffrom the ITV News team, asking if I
OL,11,Fwas available. My answer was yes, and
OL,12,Fthat's when it all started.
OL,14,FOctober 7 was a living hell for all
OL,15,Fthe residents of Gaza.
OL,17,FOn a personal level, I experienced an
OL,18,Finternal conflict between working and
OL,19,Fprotecting my family, staying by their
OL,20,Fside, and finding a safe place for
OL,21,Fthem.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/27
