OL,3,C'I had a beautiful life': Filmmaker on
OL,4,Ccapturing war in Gaza
OL,6,FMy mind stopped thinking. I thought I
OL,7,Fwouldn't reach a point of fear, but
OL,8,Fthis time was different.
OL,10,FEvery minute, I felt fear. Every time
OL,11,FI filmed people fleeing, I felt fear.
OL,12,FEvery explosion, I felt fear.
OL,14,FBeing a journalist in a field full of
OL,15,Fdeath, destruction, bodies, and the
OL,16,Foverwhelming noise breaks you inside.
OL,18,FWith every picture you take, you
OL,19,Fimagine your family in that situation,
OL,20,Fwondering if you would return home to
OL,21,Ffind them dead.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/27
