OL,3,C'I had a beautiful life': Filmmaker on
OL,4,Ccapturing war in Gaza
OL,6,FFear overwhelmed me and controlled my
OL,7,Fthoughts.
OL,9,FFive months later, in mid-February, I
OL,10,Fevacuated my family to Egypt, and from
OL,11,Fthere, the situation started to feel
OL,12,Fmore comfortable for me.
OL,14,FHowever, I still found myself in a
OL,15,Fwar. I was now thinking about how I
OL,16,Fwould survive to see my wife,
OL,17,Fchildren, mother, father, and siblings.
OL,19,FThe war on Gaza can only be described
OL,20,Fas hell.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/27
