OL,3,C'I had a beautiful life': Filmmaker on
OL,4,Ccapturing war in Gaza
OL,6,FI found out that my wife, Tahrir, was
OL,7,Fpregnant, it was during the first week
OL,8,Fof the war, around mid-October.It was
OL,9,Fa mix of conflicting emotions.
OL,11,FTahrir was scared because her previous
OL,12,Fpregnancy with our daughter, Noor, had
OL,13,Fbeen very difficult. She had anemia
OL,14,Fand was extremely exhausted during
OL,15,Fthat time.
OL,17,FSo, when she found out she was
OL,18,Fpregnant again, I became even more
OL,19,Ffrightened because the situation was
OL,20,Fcatastrophic, with bombing everywhere.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/27
