OL,3,C'I had a beautiful life': Filmmaker on
OL,4,Ccapturing war in Gaza
OL,6,FBy February, I decided they should
OL,7,Fleave. Some friends helped us get
OL,8,Ftheir names on the border crossing
OL,9,Flist within three days. But I didn't
OL,10,Fgo with them.
OL,12,FWhen they left, I felt much better. My
OL,13,Fperformance improved, and I was less
OL,14,Ftense.
OL,16,FMonths passed, and I knew I had to be
OL,17,Fby Tahrir's side for the birth. I
OL,18,Fstarted calling every day to check on
OL,19,Fthem. I made sure that Tahrir would
OL,20,Fgive birth in a good hospital in Egypt.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/27
