OL,3,C'I had a beautiful life': Filmmaker on
OL,4,Ccapturing war in Gaza
OL,6,FI was terrified that anything could
OL,7,Fhappen to her, especially since she
OL,8,Fhad been so exhausted when she was in
OL,9,FGaza due to the constant bombings and
OL,10,Fher fear for our children.
OL,12,FI feared that the baby might have
OL,13,Fdeformities due to the smell of
OL,14,Fgunpowder, bombings, the fear from the
OL,15,Fmissiles, and the gases we inhaled
OL,16,Fafter a rocket exploded, even if it
OL,17,Fwas nearby and not directly on us.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/27
