OL,3,C'I had a beautiful life': Filmmaker on
OL,4,Ccapturing war in Gaza
OL,6,FI'd seen birth defects in babies
OL,7,Fcaused by war, rockets, and that kind
OL,8,Fof stuff in Gaza, which made me think
OL,9,Fabout many things and fear that my
OL,10,Fchild might be born with deformities.
OL,12,FAt the time of birth I was on video
OL,13,Fwith my trusted friend, Ali, to
OL,14,Fwitness all the details that I should
OL,15,Fhave been there for, to witness the
OL,16,Fbirth of my child.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/27
