OL,3,C'I had a beautiful life': Filmmaker on
OL,4,Ccapturing war in Gaza
OL,6,FHonestly, the day he was born was very
OL,7,Fdifficult for me because I didn't see
OL,8,Fhim, didn't touch him, didn't hold
OL,9,Fhim, and didn't take a picture with
OL,10,Fhim, like I had done with Julia,
OL,11,FAhmad, and Noor, his older siblings.
OL,13,FIt's a hard feeling for a father who
OL,14,Fhasn't touched his child, and who is
OL,15,Ffour months old by now.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/27
