OL,3,C'I had a beautiful life': Filmmaker on
OL,4,Ccapturing war in Gaza
OL,6,FNo matter how much I try to describe
OL,7,Fmy feelings, I can't find the words to
OL,8,Fexpress what it's like for a father
OL,9,Fwho can't see his child grow up in
OL,10,Ffront of him, while living under a
OL,11,Fbarrage of missiles, artillery, and
OL,12,Fthe constant threat of death from
OL,13,Fdisease and war.
OL,15,FEvery moment I fear a rocket might
OL,16,Ffall on me, and I'll die before seeing
OL,17,Fmy child.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/27
