OL,3,C'I had a beautiful life': Filmmaker on
OL,4,Ccapturing war in Gaza
OL,6,FEvery time I'm terrified that I'll die
OL,7,Fbefore I can touch or get to know my
OL,8,Fbaby, whom I only know through
OL,9,Fpictures, seeing him grow but not
OL,10,Fbeing able to touch him.
OL,12,FDocumenting the war
OL,14,FI feel proud because I've been
OL,15,Fconveying the reality of the
OL,16,FPalestinian people to the world
OL,17,Fthrough ITV News over the past year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/27
