OL,3,C'I had a beautiful life': Filmmaker on
OL,4,Ccapturing war in Gaza
OL,6,FAs a Palestinian from Gaza, the trust
OL,7,FITV News placed in me gave me a heavy
OL,8,Fresponsibility to cover the events of
OL,9,Fthe war in Gaza.
OL,11,FMoving from Beit Hanoun in the north
OL,12,Fto Rafah in the far south, passing
OL,13,Fthrough various locations under the
OL,14,Fconstant threat of airstrikes, rocket
OL,15,Ffire, and ground invasions - hearing
OL,16,Ffighter jets overhead and knowing the
OL,17,Fdanger of being targeted was immense.
OL,19,FThroughout the year, the phases of the
OL,20,Fwar evolved.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/27
