OL,3,C'I had a beautiful life': Filmmaker on
OL,4,Ccapturing war in Gaza
OL,6,FIt started with the intense airstrikes
OL,7,Fthat posed a constant threat of death,
OL,8,Fwhere any moment you could become the
OL,9,Fnews rather than reporting it - or
OL,10,Fworse, your family could be the news.
OL,12,FProfessionally, it was challenging to
OL,13,Fcapture the full picture, especially
OL,14,Fbeing on my own.
OL,16,FOne notable change since the war
OL,17,Fstarted is the scale of killing, which
OL,18,Fsometimes reached over a thousand
OL,19,Fvictims in a day.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/27
