OL,3,C'I had a beautiful life': Filmmaker on
OL,4,Ccapturing war in Gaza
OL,6,FThe massacres, destruction, and
OL,7,Fdisplacement continue, and there is no
OL,8,Fstability, even in areas deemed "safe
OL,9,Fzones" by the Israeli army.
OL,11,FFor example, I remember evacuating
OL,12,FRafah and travelling to Khan Younis in
OL,13,Fan area declared "safe".
OL,15,FI set up a tent there, but after 10
OL,16,Fdays, due to the difficult
OL,17,Fhumanitarian conditions, I had to move
OL,18,Fagain.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/27
