OL,3,C'I had a beautiful life': Filmmaker on
OL,4,Ccapturing war in Gaza
OL,6,FA few days later, the place I had
OL,7,Fstayed was obliterated in an Israeli
OL,8,Fairstrike, killing more than 50 people.
OL,10,FThe explosion was so powerful that
OL,11,Fmany bodies were never found. This
OL,12,Fcreated a psychological burden for me
OL,13,F- imagining what would have happened
OL,14,Fif I had still been there, in my tent.
OL,16,FEven after a year, I still struggle to
OL,17,Ffind a safe place, because there is no
OL,18,Fsuch thing as a safe place here.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/27
