OL,3,C'I had a beautiful life': Filmmaker on
OL,4,Ccapturing war in Gaza
OL,6,FNo words can truly describe the
OL,7,Fhardships. Many of the memories are
OL,8,Fnow nightmares that will haunt me if I
OL,9,Fsurvive this war.
OL,11,FThere are countless stories I could
OL,12,Fshare, but one that remains with me is
OL,13,Fthat of Mohammed Abu Sahloul, a man I
OL,14,Finterviewed just minutes before he was
OL,15,Fshot by the Israeli army. The memory
OL,16,Fof that moment still haunts me.
OL,18,FIt took me three days to find his
OL,19,Ffamily after the frequent
OL,20,Fdisplacements.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/27
