OL,3,C'I had a beautiful life': Filmmaker on
OL,4,Ccapturing war in Gaza
OL,6,FIt's an incident that can only be
OL,7,Fdescribed as a war crime, one of many
OL,8,Funtold horrors that haven't been
OL,9,Fdocumented due to the dangers of
OL,10,Freporting here.
OL,12,FNever-ending challenges
OL,14,FMy family were reluctant to leave,
OL,15,Funwilling to abandon their home and
OL,16,Fmemories. The house wasn't just bricks
OL,17,Fand mortar - it was where my son Ahmed
OL,18,Ftook his first steps, where my
OL,19,Fdaughter Julia had her first bath, and
OL,20,Fwhere Noor called me "Baba" for the
OL,21,Ffirst time.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G20/27
