OL,3,C'I had a beautiful life': Filmmaker on
OL,4,Ccapturing war in Gaza
OL,6,FIt wasn't easy to leave, knowing I
OL,7,Fmight never return.
OL,9,FI moved six times in the first four
OL,10,Fmonths of the war, each move more
OL,11,Fdifficult than the last.
OL,13,FLogistically, it was nearly impossible
OL,14,Fto find safe routes for movement. Fuel
OL,15,Fwas scarce and expensive, and car
OL,16,Fparts were even harder to come by.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G21/27
