OL,3,C'I had a beautiful life': Filmmaker on
OL,4,Ccapturing war in Gaza
OL,6,FMoving at night was terrifying, and
OL,7,Feven coordinating with medics for
OL,8,Fnight-time coverage was risky, as
OL,9,Fthere were no lights or electricity
OL,10,Fafter 6pm.
OL,12,FSupplies were hard to come by - water,
OL,13,Ffood, and basic necessities were in
OL,14,Fshort supply. Even getting a camera or
OL,15,Fany filming equipment was impossible
OL,16,Fif my gear was damaged.
