OL,3,C'I had a beautiful life': Filmmaker on
OL,4,Ccapturing war in Gaza
OL,6,FOne of the other challenges I faced
OL,7,Fwas the internet outages and
OL,8,Fdisruptions to mobile phone service,
OL,9,Fthe local telecommunications network,
OL,10,Fand even the landline. This was the
OL,11,Fhardest time for us in terms of
OL,12,Fcommunication.
OL,14,FIt exposed us to danger and could have
OL,15,Fkilled us at any moment as we searched
OL,16,Ffor an internet source, tried to find
OL,17,Fsolutions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G23/27
