OL,3,C'I had a beautiful life': Filmmaker on
OL,4,Ccapturing war in Gaza
OL,6,FWe used to go to elevated places to
OL,7,Fcatch a signal, just to connect to the
OL,8,Finternet and let Yara, my colleague in
OL,9,Fthe office, know that I was still
OL,10,Falive.
OL,12,FSeveral times people carrying SIM
OL,13,Fcards were targeted, so every time I
OL,14,Fwent to connect to the internet, I had
OL,15,Fto think a hundred times about how to
OL,16,Fplace the phone connected to the
OL,17,Finternet far from me and use another
OL,18,Fphone as a hotspot.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G24/27
