OL,3,C'I had a beautiful life': Filmmaker on
OL,4,Ccapturing war in Gaza
OL,6,FI tried my best to stay in touch, send
OL,7,Fout reports, and reassure my family
OL,8,Fand my news crew that I was still
OL,9,Falive, that I was still working.
OL,11,FI made sure to reach out at every
OL,12,Fopportunity when I could get a
OL,13,Fconnection. Every time we managed to
OL,14,Fget a signal, it felt like a
OL,15,Frevelation.
OL,17,FWhen people would hear the phone ring,
OL,18,Fthey'd be shocked, asking: "How did
OL,19,Fyou get a signal? How did you get an
OL,20,Finternet?"
