OL,3,C'I had a beautiful life': Filmmaker on
OL,4,Ccapturing war in Gaza
OL,6,FThis was one of the hardest moments we
OL,7,Flived through, and I pray it never
OL,8,Fhappens again. I just want them to
OL,9,Fknow, at least, whether I'm alive or
OL,10,Fdead.
OL,12,FThe Najjar family comes to mind as an
OL,13,Fexample of the resilience of the
OL,14,Fpeople here. After their house was
OL,15,Fdestroyed, they preferred to return to
OL,16,Fits ruins, despite the dangers,
OL,17,Fbecause the alternative - living in
OL,18,Fdisease-ridden refugee camps - was
OL,19,Funbearable.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G26/27
