OL,3,C'I had a beautiful life': Filmmaker on
OL,4,Ccapturing war in Gaza
OL,6,FTheir daughter, Sarah, who is blind,
OL,7,Fposes an added challenge during any
OL,8,Fsudden displacement, as no one knows
OL,9,Fhow she will react or if she will even
OL,10,Fbe able to find her way to safety.
OL,12,FTheir story is one of many untold
OL,13,Ftragedies, and countless others remain
OL,14,Fundocumented, far worse than what the
OL,15,Fworld has seen.
OL,17,FThere are many untold stories, and we
OL,18,Fstrive every day to tell them to the
OL,19,Fworld.
